headline: Cognex, Rumble, CECO Environmental, Jabil, and Jacobs Solutions Shares Are Falling, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the morning session after a surprisingly weak U.S. jobs report was released, fueling concerns about a slowing economy.
